    "body": "      The value of DWITH_PYTHON:BOOL is wrong when the python is not used.\r\n\r\n```\r\n        if '+python' in spec:\r\n            args.extend([\r\n                \"-DWITH_PYTHON:BOOL=ON\",\r\n                \"-DWITH_PYTHON_INCLUDE:PATH=%s\" % spec['python'].prefix,\r\n            ])\r\n        else:\r\n            args.append('-DWITH_PYTHON:BOOL=ON')\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
